ary acceleration was specified to occur in the vicinity of the\nintersection between the trajectories of the H-alpha jet and X-ray jet observed\nby Hinode/XRT. We propose that a fundamental cause of this phenomenon is the\nmagnetic reconnection involving the plasmoid in the observed jet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Oct 2017 18:18:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
