es that many absorption lines are affected by- or form in- the\noverflowing stream material veiling the WD, making the analysis of the WD\nspectra more difficult.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Oct 2017 22:48:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
