ralized) lambda-deformation to construct new\nintegrable backgrounds depending on several continuous parameters and study\nanalytical properties of the such deformations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Oct 2017 22:55:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Nov 2017 00:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-28"}
