 can\nimprove the bit error rate performance by exploiting the diversity gain.\nMoreover, Bregman ADMM method outperforms the belief consensus-based algorithm\nin noisy inter-user links.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Oct 2017 03:32:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-25"}
